# ТВОЙ ХОД — роутер агента

## Карта проекта

- **Код и API**: [`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md)
- **Продукт**: [`docs/foundation/SPEC_PRODUCT.md`](docs/foundation/SPEC_PRODUCT.md)
- **Конвейер docs**: [`docs/agents/SKILL_DOC_MAP.md`](docs/agents/SKILL_DOC_MAP.md), [`docs/DOCUMENTATION_SYSTEM.md`](docs/DOCUMENTATION_SYSTEM.md)
- **Скиллы**: [`docs/agents/CURSOR_SKILLS.md`](docs/agents/CURSOR_SKILLS.md), [`docs/agents/SKILLS_PHASE_CONTENT_AND_DATA.md`](docs/agents/SKILLS_PHASE_CONTENT_AND_DATA.md), [`.cursor/skills/catalog.yaml`](.cursor/skills/catalog.yaml) (`tier`)
- **Баланс / пороги**: [`docs/vision/ideas/game-balance-thresholds-and-constraints.md`](docs/vision/ideas/game-balance-thresholds-and-constraints.md)
- **MQX**: [`frontend-react/src/components/mqx/DESIGN_WORKFLOW.md`](frontend-react/src/components/mqx/DESIGN_WORKFLOW.md) — читать **целиком** перед новым UI (исключение: hotfix без смены дизайна)

